====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[rinse]]; to [[wash]] [[away]]
# to [[discard]]; to [[eliminate]] through [[competition]] or [[selection]]
# [[arrogant]]
#* {{zh-x|伯-石 之 汰 也，一 為{wéi}-禮 於 晉，猶 荷{hè} 其 祿。|As '''overreaching''' as he had been, Gongsun Duan [Boshi] nevertheless managed with one good performance of ritual in Jin to come away laden with rewards.|ref=Zuozhuan-D}}
# [[extravagant]], [[excessive]]
#* {{zh-x|皆 所以 示 諸侯 汰 也，諸侯 所-由 棄 命 也。今 君 以 汰，無 乃 不-濟 乎？|In each case the ceremonies became occasions on which they displayed their '''excesses''' to the princes and were the reason the princes ignored their commands. Now that you are acting '''excessively''', is it not the case that you will fail to prevail?|ref=Zuozhuan-D}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} do not; [[don't]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} [[forget it]]; [[forget]] [[about]] it

